# Testing

| Type | Required for |
|------|----------------|
| Unit | Business rules, calculations, validators |
| Integration | DB, API, storage, SMS, payment |
| End-to-end | Critical owner and booking flows |
| Security | Authorization and abuse controls |
| Concurrency | Capacity, booking and payment races |
| Regression | Existing affected flows |

- Do not finish behavior changes without relevant tests.
- Cover success, failure and edge cases for changed logic.
- Report: tests run, passed, skipped and remaining risk.
- Prefer fixing the product over hiding failures or skipping gates without approval.
